OOC: No I wont bother with Slaughter, but next time could you give me
some time to post with the base before you did all the things you did.
There are some internal defenses now, and there would have been lots to
meet you in the entrance now that you fired on the base. Could you go
back to where you inserted your probe into the computer

BIC:

The computer had realised it had an none Decepticon in its databanks,
and redirected internal defenses to one area. The most heavy duty one
were in the main control room. It emited a shock of 100 000 volts
through its socket, into the intruder.
